flowchart TD
    A[Create first App Service] --> B{Does app have Windows-only dependencies?}
    B -->|Yes| C[Choose Windows]
    B -->|No| D[Choose Linux]

    C --> E{Need direct control over image/OS packages?}
    D --> E

    E -->|Yes| F[Container deployment]
    E -->|No| G[Code deployment]

    F --> H{Learning/experiment environment?}
    G --> H

    H -->|Yes| I[Free or Shared]
    H -->|No| J{Is customer traffic or operational stability important?}

    J -->|No| K[Basic]
    J -->|Yes| L{Need deployment slots/autoscale/operational safeguards?}

    L -->|Yes| M[Standard]
    L -->|No| K

    M --> N{Need advanced networking, more memory, stronger isolation?}
    N -->|Yes| O[Consider Premium]
    N -->|No| P[Keep Standard]

